inside the warehouse.

151
00:06:08,883 --> 00:06:10,017
How long?

152
00:06:10,085 --> 00:06:12,219
Meet me outside CTU
in 30 minutes.

153
00:06:12,287 --> 00:06:14,221
ARLO: Did you take care
of your situation?

154
00:06:14,289 --> 00:06:15,923
Situation?

155
