there, on the roof.

237
00:10:08,056 --> 00:10:10,557
Once the money is
in our account,

238
00:10:10,625 --> 00:10:13,393
they'll bring him back here,
we will talk.

239
00:10:13,461 --> 00:10:15,863
I'll give him a call.

240
00:10:17,899 --> 00:10:19,533
It's good to see you.

241
00:10:22,470 --> 00:10:25,939
