537
00:23:31,741 --> 00:23:32,941
Miss Perfect?

538
00:23:33,009 --> 00:23:33,942
She seems
distracted,

539
00:23:34,010 --> 00:23:35,877
always making excuses to leave.

540
00:23:35,945 --> 00:23:37,612
